column18:
This extended necklace is adorned with recycled sterling silver
and turquoise beads. At 92cm, it can be worn as a single chain, or
wrapped around twice for a double-layered look that makes a
colourful statement all year long.

Necklace circumference 91cm/ 36&quot;
Cast Bead Length Approximately 9cm/3.5&quot;

A super-fine, plaited texture chain featuring delicate hand
crafted twists. The adjustable clasp means you can style this as a
choker or a necklace. Perfect for layering, adding a pendant, or
wearing solo.

Necklace circumference adjustable 38cm, 41cm or 43cm/ 15&quot;, 16&quot;
or 17&quot;
